Musicians Folarin ‘Falz’ Falana and Ric Hassani have joined fans to react to the ongoing wedding between Adekunle Gold and Simisola Ogunleye. In "Music" Since the news broke that popular singers, Adekunle Gold and Simi got married secretly, they have kept mum on the matter. In "Entertainment" As the anticipation increases over Adekunle Gold’s debut album, the Orente sensation is doing everything possible to get his name on the lips of music lovers. In "Entertainment"